Title: TV Classic Westerns: Bat Masterson/Death Valley Days/The Rifleman/Wagon

reviewText: Bits and pieces of old classic TV show/movies.It enjoyable.  If youre expecting more rifleman episodes, they arent here.Only the standard two  they put on most of these style of westerns dvds.
Title: TV Classic Westerns: Bat Masterson/Death Valley Days/The Rifleman/Wagon

reviewText: TV Classic Westerns: Bat Masterson/Death Valley Days/The Rifleman/Wagon (1999) was very entertaining.  I would like to have seen more Death Valley Days and Bat Masterson since they are not available on television in the Atlanta area.  I recommend this item.

reviewText: This brings back such pleasant memories from my childhood!My Brother and I laying in front of theTV waiting for our Westerns to come on!Good Quality and very entertaining!
Title: TV Classic Westerns: Bat Masterson/Death Valley Days/The Rifleman/Wagon

reviewText: I don't know why the other reviews rated this disc so highly.  The package may say it is digitally MASTERED but it is NOT digitally REmastered!  There was no restoration work done on this disc whatsoever, and it shows.  The quality is barely passable, and probably was dubbed off older vhs tapes.  I think the other reviewers were just so ecstatic that these episodes were even available on DVD that their judgement got the best of them.  In summary, if you can find this disc for a couple of bucks go for it, otherwise, you'd be better off getting the Rifleman and Wagon Train on other DVD editions.
summary: Not as good as the other reviewers said!
